docs/compliance/model-cards/

# Marketing / sales / support — PRODUCT & GTM SOURCES (policy, 2026-07):
# These are source-of-truth IP — GEO research packs, the sales playbook, landing
# copy, content calendar, value ladder, SEO/keyword research, and the lead-magnet
# sources the paid PDFs in apps/web/public/downloads are built from. They MUST
# live in git so the founder's laptop is not the only copy. Do NOT re-ignore
# docs/marketing, docs/sales, or docs/support. If a genuinely ephemeral,
# regenerable artifact ever lands under here, add a narrow, commented exception
# for that specific path — never blanket-ignore the directories again.

# Learning docs (institutional knowledge — MUST be committed, never ignored)
# docs/learning/ is intentionally NOT listed here so it is always tracked by git

# Compiled artifacts must never live in src/ (they shadow .ts in vitest)
packages/*/src/**/*.js
packages/*/src/**/*.js.map
packages/*/src/**/*.d.ts
apps/*/src/**/*.js
apps/*/src/**/*.js.map
